--- 敏感配置文件 (极其重要) ---

保护你的 DeepSeek API Key 不被上传

config.json
config.example.json
*.env

--- Python 后端 ---

pycache/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.venv/
venv/
ENV/
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/

--- Godot 引擎 ---

忽略 Godot 自动生成的导入数据和缓存

.godot/
*.import
export_presets.cfg

如果你不希望导出的二进制文件被追踪

*.exe

*.pck

--- 编辑器与系统 ---

.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

--- 临时文件与日志 ---

*.log
backend/output_godot/
godot_plugin/output/


# Godot 缓存
godot_project/.godot/
godot_project/*.import
godot_project/export_presets.cfg
godot_project/*.translation